// Mended Biome Blade
TrueDefaultAttunement: {
	Name: Pure Clarity
	Function:
		'''
		Fires a weak sword beam that crushes enemy defenses
		Landing three true melee hits charges a powerful lunge, unleashed when you stop swinging the sword
		Enemies struck by the lunge are marked with a sigil that sword beams will home in on
		'''
}

TrueHotAttunement: {
	Name: Arid Grandeur
	Function:
		'''
		Conjure searing blades in front of you that get larger with enemy hits
		The blades will bounce you off of tiles while in the air
		Releasing after the blades are fully charged sends them hurtling forwards to shred your foes
		'''
}

TrueColdAttunement: {
	Name: Biting Embrace
	Function:
		'''
		Perform a 3 strike combo with a glacial blade, with the final strike freezing foes for a split second
		Harmful lingering glacial mist is released on each swing
		'''
}

TrueTropicalAttunement: {
	Name: Grovetender's Touch
	Function:
		'''
		Throw out the blade using a vine whip
		Striking enemies with the tip of the whip as it cracks guarantees a critical hit
		Spreading vines sprout from critical strikes, which can hit up to three targets
		'''
}

TrueEvilAttunement: {
	Name: Decay's Retort
	Function:
		'''
		Lunge forward with a ghostly rapier projection, bouncing away from struck targets and leeching their life
		Landing three strikes without touching the ground turns your next attack into an empowered dash thrust
		'''
}

HolyAttunement: {
	Name: Heaven's Might
	Function:
		'''
		Swing the sword around you, accelerating and dealing more damage over time
		Once swung for long enough, releasing hurls the sword towards your cursor for a short time
		Striking an enemy with the hurled sword at maximum power causes an astral monolith to erupt from them
		'''
}

// True Biome Blade
WhirlwindAttunement: {
	Name: Swordsmith's Pride
	Function:
		'''
		Hold <left> to swing the sword around you, accelerating and dealing more damage over time
		Homing astral energies are wildly fired around you while swinging
		Once swung for long enough, releasing hurls the sword towards your cursor
		The hurled sword erupts into astral monoliths on enemy hits
		'''
	PassiveDesc: Striking enemies occasionally spawns homing astral bombers that spread the Astral Infection
}

FlailBladeAttunement: {
	Name: Lamentations of the Chained
	Function:
		'''
		Lash out with a flurry of chained blades
		Striking enemies with the tip of the blades guarantees a critical strike
		Critical strikes send out extra phantom chains which latch onto multiple targets
		'''
	PassiveDesc: An enchanted chain hook floats near you which spins and freezes enemies while dealing damage
}

SuperPogoAttunement: {
	Name: Sanguine Fury
	Function:
		'''
		Conjure molten blades in front of you that get larger with enemy hits
		The blades will bounce you off of tiles while in the air
		Releasing sends the charged blades hurtling forwards like a wheel
		Attacking immediately after throwing the blade launches you toward it, slicing through enemies and healing you
		'''
	PassiveDesc: Striking enemies will rarely heal you
}

ShockwaveAttunement: {
	Name: Earthen Tides
	Function:
		'''
		Charge an earth-shattering lunge, release to unleash a devastating blow
		Homing sword beams are emitted as the sword charges up
		Striking an enemy with the lunge creates a shockwave and marks them with an armor crunching sigil that attracts sword beam homing
		Striking the earth with the lunge will cause several blasts of dust to erupt around you
		'''
	PassiveDesc: Periodically emit large shock waves while attacking
}

